ESocket states
#Parent ESocket_
State	Meaning
#Line
1	Trying to look up address
2	Trying to connect
3	Listening
4	Connected and usable
-1	Host lookup failed (no such host)
-2	Resolver failure (no response)
-3	Resolver error (not running)
-4	No sockets left
-5	Host is unreachable
-6	Connection refused
-7	Bind error (someone is already listening)
-8	Nobody has connected (to a listening socket)
